caption:
Antony single-handedly destroyed Fiorentina & legendary DDG to take Real Betis to the UECL Final! 💚🤍

Antony dropped the greatest performance in the history of the UEFA Europa Conference League Knockouts with his stunning goals! 

🗣️ David De Gea: “I trained with Antony 1,000 times and he never scored a goal with his right foot in any training session.”

“I’m happy for him because he was coming from a difficult moment at United and now he’s showing the best of himself.”

Antony has led Real Betis to their FIRST-EVER EUROPEAN FINAL! 👏🐐

Just GOAT things!
